  3.683728411792903*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f3febb1c-5cc4-4b05-b3e5-\
462296ba04d5"],

Cell["\<\
EventSpecifications[status, events, options] with
status = {checkstatus,chronstatus,nestedliststatus, \
standstatus,expintegerrepstatus}.
Each of the statusflags = {implement, done}
implement = True signals implementation to proceed.
done = True signals implementation has been done.
* checkstatus indicates that all event specifications have been checked and \
are valid.
* chronstatus refers to standardization of RtoL chronology.
* nestedliststatus refers to implementation of any nested lists.
* standstatus refers to the standardization of all events. 
* expintegerrepstatus refers to expansion of Repeat with integer loops\
\>", "Text",
 InitializationCell->True,
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.683728307124783*^9, 3.683728570664878*^9}, {
   3.683729645037865*^9, 3.683729675555797*^9}, {3.683784071922155*^9, 
