Cell["\<\
set status to show that all events have been standardized (except in the case \
where an embedded EventSpecifications object is created). \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.691054615127749*^9, 3.691054624399317*^9}, {
  3.6910548810734673`*^9, 
  3.691054903782198*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"613f7e19-cf83-461b-8ba2-\
beb31339a254"],

Cell["\<\
the FurtherEventSpecificationPatterns option of EventSpecifications may be \
set outside this package in order to implement new EventSpecifications \
definitions. This is done in the package Events`PulseSequence\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.6919418208418293`*^9, 3.691941894025577*^9}, {
  3.692171053567739*^9, 
  3.692171063412379*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"337f35ca-1ba6-4b7d-bd86-\
2775315f00de"],

Cell["\<\
when an EventList is the argument, the chronology must be handled carefully. \
\
\>", "Text",
