Cell["\<\
invert the Chronology if required. 
The intended value of Chronology is specified as an input to the routine.
Indicate that standard chronology has been implemented (if necessary by \
inverting the order of elements) by using the flag \
StandardizedChronologyImplemented.\
\>", "Text",
